Burden of disease attributable to suboptimal diet, metabolic risks and low 
physical activity in Ethiopia and comparison with Eastern sub-Saharan African 
countries, 1990-2015: findings from the Global Burden of Disease Study 2015.

Melaku YA(1)(2), Wassie MM(3)(4), Gill TK(5), Zhou SJ(4), Tessema GA(6)(7), 
