Expanding indication of padeliporfin (WST11) vascular-targeted photodynamic 
therapy: results of prostate cancer Latin-American multicenter study.

[Article in English, Spanish]

Rodriguez-Rivera JA(1), Rodriguez-Lay R(2), Zegarra-Montes L(3), Benzaghou F(4), 
Gaillac B(4), Azzouzi AR(5), Reis LO(6), Palma P(7).

Author information:
(1)Departamento de Urología, Hospital General de Occidente, S.S.J., Guadalajara, 
